    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so exhausting though. all that \"finding purpose\" you're talking about... it feels like so much unnecessary work for someone who's already empty. if the part of me that actually lived is dead, isn't the rest of it just... dragging a corpse around? it feels like there's no dignity in just lingering around when there's nothing left to give.",
